Usage:
install: spkg install script-name (installs scripts from this repo: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Pan00Pernicek/scriptpkg/master/repo-index, be free to pr or make issue to add another package)
sync script from url: spkg sync script-url (you will be asked for name that you want save script as)
update script: spkg update script-name
remove script: spkg remove script-name
list scripts: spkg list (if you install scripts with sudo then you need also use sudo here)
more info: https://github.com/Pan00Pernicek/scriptpkg
